nihon94 wrote on 5/1/2014, 6:03 PM

I had noticed some time Magix users wanted to know the volume number, genres or instruments of the Magix Soundpool therefore, I decided to compile this PDF e-book.

In this PDF you can find soundpools from 9 to 20 with their volume number, genre and instruments.

If you find any error please let me know also leave your comments.

nihon94
